        "content": "<p>Did the syntax highlighting colours on zulip change for anyone else recently? Here's what it looks like on my computer, starting today:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/GeSs4W0iMATH9SnaSvwdveIB/Screenshot-2023-12-06-at-06-22-33-750-Is-there-code-for-X-Lean-Zulip.png\">Screenshot-2023-12-06-at-06-22-33-750-Is-there-code-for-X-Lean-Zulip.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/GeSs4W0iMATH9SnaSvwdveIB/Screenshot-2023-12-06-at-06-22-33-750-Is-there-code-for-X-Lean-Zulip.png\" title=\"Screenshot-2023-12-06-at-06-22-33-750-Is-there-code-for-X-Lean-Zulip.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/3121/GeSs4W0iMATH9SnaSvwdveIB/Screenshot-2023-12-06-at-06-22-33-750-Is-there-code-for-X-Lean-Zulip.png\"></a></div>",
